備註 Remarks





基本素養 Basic Literacy
□ 社會關懷
 Care for society.
 

核心能力 Competence
□ 宏觀地球科學專業知識及實務現象觀測
 Professional knowledge in Geosciences and practical surveys.
□ 地球科學專業文獻資料蒐集及實驗設計與整合操作規劃知能
 Professional literature in Geosciences, experimental design, and integrated knowledge of operation.
□ 地球科學專業知能與科技應用及量化檢測分析能力
 Professional knowledge in Geosciences and techniques for quantitative analysis.
□ 外語溝通能力
 Communication in foreign languages.
■ 團隊溝通、協調及領導能力
 Communication, negotiation and leadership on the team.
■ 整合應用地球科學產業專業科技知能及跨領域能力
 Integration technical skills and knowledge for geological industry and cross-disciplinary ability.
■ 積極?獵科學新知
 Explore new science knowledge.
■ 關懷自然環境及生態保育
 Care for natural environment and ecological conservation.
 

課程概述 Course Description
       以地球碳循環探討環境之變遷，講述相關環境研究議題與應用。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
以地球碳循環探討環境之變遷相關環境研究議題與應用瞭解地球碳循環與相關地球化學研究應用 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1green-house effect2ozone depletion3“missing” CO24primary production versus new production5Fe hypothesis6uptake of anthropogenic CO2 by the ocean 7paleo-productivity8paleo-temperature9ice volume & sea level change10Milankovitch theory and marine isotope record11paleo-deep water circulation12Devil’s Hole isotope record13dating of aragonite in marine sediment cores14Younger Dryas cooling and Henrich events15Oscheger-Dansgaard events16bipolar oscillation17tropical-extratropical interaction18modeling the atmosphere-ocean systems 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


